Marker for the root of the bespoke-git-workflow-commands source repo.

The test/ scripts refuse to run whenever this marker is present in the repo
they would operate on, so they can never wipe this repo's own git history.

To run the tests, copy the test/ folder into a disposable repo and run it from
there (see the Testing section of the README). Do not delete this file, and do
not copy it into a test sandbox.

